creator: Swish App
descriptionHtml:
Pay for your shopping with the Swish payment app. Download your Swish app and discover secure cash-free spending.

Swish is wallet-neutral and does not have a wallet for consumers or merchants but rather integrates to the various
existing wallets, banks and card schemes in facilitating payments from a consumers funding source directly to a
merchant’s account.
descriptionShort: Swish is a Payment Platform, facilitates payments from a consumer to a merchant.
